Move Right into This Bright and Spacious Semi-Attached Home Featuring 6 Bedrooms and 3 Full Bathrooms on a Sunny Beach Block. Private Parking in Driveway. French Doors to yard.  1 Bedroom/ 1Bath Rental equals Guaranteed Income.  Accessible to all (Beach, Shopping, YMCA, Restaurants, Schools, Parks).  Truly a Turnkey - Don't Forget to Bring Your Bathing Suit.
